Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前  有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底两万哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌懦弱的人  无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作梦之前  我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音乐盒开启  发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前  有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  forget  to  try  in  mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时值西元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了逃离企图夺取\N"蔚蓝之水"的邪恶三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸在海上漂流的强\N娜蒂亚与大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到美国战舰的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是战舰却在\N神秘大海兽的攻击下重创
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强他们也被迫\N再度回到海上漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#04  万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个孩子究竟是到哪去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韩森\N我们要在这里待到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上藉由星星就能晓得位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时再到最近的岛屿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算穿那身装扮到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到我能洗澡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下身为堂堂绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因为炎热就穿着邋遢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就烦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我都遇不到好男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的运气会这么差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来吧\N都不像你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是跟我在一起\N才害你有这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死前我要先向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起我觉得很快乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,我是在跟大王道歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上抓条大鱼给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,可是我不吃鱼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在对大王说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那头海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又折回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,它是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一动也不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚,娜蒂亚呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙并不是海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由人类制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两名遇难者已经收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这就是海兽的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潜水艇,潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜水艇?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以自由潜入海里的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个大发明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击沉战舰与你爸爸的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会就是这艘船?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是排水口吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭完新型战舰之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能搭到这么棒的潜水艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太走运了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,这并没有打铆钉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么焊接的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长,右舷两点钟方向\N出现微弱磁气反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离太过遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是那艘战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得,总之先接近再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解,引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引擎的声音,要启航了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两舷全速,路线变更027
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这具引擎已经挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁气反应未出现改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对速度目前约32节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死区虽然让你溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我的运气似乎还很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船长\N请问要如何处置遇难者?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长,是你开口说要救人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-交由你处理吧\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个孩子似乎满坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您明明是讨厌所有的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,这艘船为什么要救我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们被困在海上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们也跟那3个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了想拿到"蔚蓝之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝之水!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样多疑不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比随便相信人好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有门把\N但这个应该是门没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拜托这艘船上的人\N让我参观船舱内部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会伤害你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船可能是那只海中怪兽耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,连面都还没见过\N说话这么失礼不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对别人客气一点\N这样对自己也比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位公主名叫娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我则是王子,名叫强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗,谢谢你,强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚,他人的好意\N你就接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚,走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以参观船舱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且"蔚蓝之水"没有发光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示没有危险,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好窄又好奇怪的走廊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬梆梆又古怪的门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你就是艾丽朵拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N你们先把湿衣服换下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确,这个房间好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为房里有冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷气?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,夏天也能让房间\N保持凉爽的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天还能这么凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是人类最大的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是怎样的构造?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先去冲个澡\N换上干净的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲澡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是热可可亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好神奇的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是,这是科学的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确\N这艘船根本就是科学的精华嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪个国家的船?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不像是法国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是英国,还是美国?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不属于任何一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是海盗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是追捕海盗的那一方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要戴上那种面具?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没看过我们的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回到陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法告诉他人\N你们见过什么人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一群已经和陆地\N断绝关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你们能将\N在这里见过的事全都忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意让我们回去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我们目前正在追踪\N重要的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间放你们下船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定会负起责任\N将你们送回陆地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船长也把你们交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得"尼莫"在拉丁文里\N代表着"什么人都不是"的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你懂得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是他的本名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却是最适合船长的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艾丽朵拉也不是你的本名吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就任凭你们想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天会送两次餐点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然少了点\N但就先忍忍罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见,你们要好好相处喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗"蔚蓝之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被卖到马戏团的时候\N就带在身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说我身上就只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候你几岁?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得…那时候我还很小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有"蔚蓝之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成为我寻找家人的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熄灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是代表晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不晓得\N现在是白天还是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连这艘船要去哪里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,这应该是叫我们该睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,你醒着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得这艘船不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾丽朵拉对我们很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会平白无故对别人好\N一定另有企图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…遇到的人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我想发明了\N这么厉害潜水艇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们或许是害了你爸爸的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不一定是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要凡事都往不好的方面想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先请他们\N让我参观这艘船的机械设备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再慢慢想以后的事就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,前半部停机库的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?有办法修吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把引擎换掉也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,没错\N就照你的意思改装
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是到这里来之后吃的\N第5顿玉米汤、面包及牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说已经3天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到什么时候才能出去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论按哪个键都打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被锁住了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,我想请他们\N先让我参观船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们连脸都不肯让你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会让你参观船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是艾丽朵拉说的冷气吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长,请立刻前来舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,舰首2点钟方向\N发现引擎声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-立刻进行测距\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位32度,距离9200
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是石像鬼的潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约8节,正朝本舰航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被发现了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动声纳呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并未发出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要攻击吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,先按兵不动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-以距离5千追踪敌舰\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要找出\N石像鬼的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定接触位置还有300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近至8800
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,在被对方声纳发现前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行无声潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰停止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行无声潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船停下来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水深固定于120
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两舷平衡一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动悬吊,切换完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度3节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消磁装置,开始运作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰启动防爆鱼雷防御
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰启动防爆鱼雷防御
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防水闸门封闭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有水密舱门固定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防爆准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熄灯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的情况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,距离7500
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位及速度不变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是推进器遭战舰破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是陷阱?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离接近至7000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离接近至5000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离3000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是那两个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度、方位皆不变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未发出主动声纳,距离1200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以肉眼确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将通过本舰上方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有东西正从上面经过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深水炸弹,从正上方过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎全开,垂直上升
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受损情况呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1辅助引擎中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首右舷中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进水极轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从7时至7时5分方向\N逐渐远离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离800,速度12节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让它跑了\N左舷回转160度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦测到鱼雷发射声\N4枚,距离1200
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速回避
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼雷防御
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受损情形呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未遭击中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并无进水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压载一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉回水平位置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到,声波混乱无法辨识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航海仪器及电罗经也全部失常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船身周围遭强力磁场覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼雷之中似乎含有妨碍物质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在移动会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰停止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得重头来过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外头,该说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见到太阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我还是没能参观到船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒,变成水上飞机了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是鹦鹉螺号和我所送的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹦鹉螺号?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里往南飞会有座大岛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有船开往法国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在飞机里放了罗盘、地图\N以及一点食物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼莫船长给的时间\N只剩下5分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你还在做什么,快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待续)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:24:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自语  仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try  安慰的话语\N是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.90,0:24:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.20,0:24:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.84,0:24:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.59,0:25:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.33,0:25:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载着我们两个人\N与一只动物的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.79,0:25:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然遭到攻击而坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.76,0:25:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本和平的岛屿\N遭到侵略者占领
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为一座恐怖之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.47,0:25:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚,这孩子还活着\N她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.07,0:25:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉…振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底两万哩  下一回\N“玛莉之岛”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.88,0:25:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要看喔\N-要看喔
